com.khalsa_ji.ems

Class Employee

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.khalsa_ji.ems.Employee

  • @Entity
public class Employee
extends java.lang.Object
    The class Employee defines various real world properties of an employee in any organisation, methods to play around with those defined properties and also acts as a database entity.
